Class FreezerVisitor

java.lang.Object
  |

        |
        +--JavaLog.visitor.TransformerVisitor

              +--JavaLog.visitor.FreezerVisitor
public class FreezerVisitor
extends TransformerVisitor

This class encapsulates an abstract transformation performed on the elements of an Prolog structure. You can create new transformations by defining subclasses of this class.
